tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE keypoints (id INT PRIMARY KEY, image_id INT, keypoint_data BYTEA);
CREATE TABLE descriptors (id INT PRIMARY KEY, keypoint_id INT, descriptor_data BYTEA);
CREATE TABLE images (id INT PRIMARY KEY, image_name TEXT, image_data BYTEA);
CREATE TABLE matches (id INT PRIMARY KEY, image1_id INT, image2_id INT, similarity_score FLOAT);
CREATE TABLE registrations (id INT PRIMARY KEY, image_id INT, registration_data JSON);
